overview: She's such a giving teen that she's willing to do anything to help her friends get jobs. If you were an employer, would you be able to turn her down if she offered up her body in trade?  Ivy Aura - Tells him she has a crush on him and then says that her parents won't be home for awhile.  Dolly Leigh - A babysitter with her hand caught in the drain is an opportunity!  Niki Snow - Couldn't hide her crush any longer after her client treated her so nicely!  Charity Crawford - Lives up to her name by offering up her body.
title: Homewrecking Babysitters 9
